{
  "work_slug": "the-maltese-falcon-novel-version-by-dashiell-hammett",
  "work_title": "Maltese Falcon; Novel Version",
  "work_author": "Dashiell Hammett",
  "audio_file": "audio-01",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/themaltesefalconnovel_2603_librivox/maltesefalcon_01_hammett.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "Spade and Archer",
  "reader_name": "NLizer",
  "page_num": 1,
  "page_total": 4,
  "page_start_sec": 0.608,
  "page_end_sec": 262.3,
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.685,
  "corrected": "claude",
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 0.608,
      "end": 1.02,
      "text": "CHAPTER I."
    },
    {
      "start": 1.26,
      "end": 2.44,
      "text": "OF THE MALTESE FALCON."
    },
    {
      "start": 1.44,
      "end": 6.88,
      "text": "This is a LibriVox recording. All LibriVox recordings are in"
    },
    {
      "start": 6.88,
      "end": 12.42,
      "text": " the public domain. For more information or to volunteer, please visit LibriVox.org."
    },
    {
      "start": 13.48,
      "end": 17.48,
      "text": " The Maltese Falcon by Dashiell Hammett. Spade and Archer."
    },
    {
      "start": 18.39,
      "end": 20.94,
      "text": "SAMUEL SPADE'S jaw was long and bony,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 21.12,
      "end": 24.86,
      "text": "his chin a jutting v under the more flexible v"
    },
    {
      "start": 25.08,
      "end": 25.6,
      "text": "of his mouth."
    },
    {
      "start": 26.56,
      "end": 28.34,
      "text": "His nostrils curved back to make another,"
    },
    {
      "start": 28.34,
      "end": 29.0,
      "text": "smaller, v."
    },
    {
      "start": 30.22,
      "end": 31.44,
      "text": "His yellow-grey eyes were"
    },
    {
      "start": 31.52,
      "end": 31.98,
      "text": "horizontal."
    },
    {
      "start": 33.06,
      "end": 34.58,
      "text": "The v _motif_ was picked up again"
    },
    {
      "start": 34.74,
      "end": 37.78,
      "text": "by thickish brows rising outward from twin creases"
    },
    {
      "start": 37.94,
      "end": 39.02,
      "text": "above a hooked nose,"
    },
    {
      "start": 39.24,
      "end": 42.8,
      "text": "and his pale brown hair grew down—from high flat temples—"
    },
    {
      "start": 43.36,
      "end": 44.46,
      "text": "in a point on his forehead."
    },
    {
      "start": 45.2,
      "end": 47.66,
      "text": "He looked rather pleasantly like a blond satan."
    },
    {
      "start": 48.24,
      "end": 50.26,
      "text": "He said to Effie Perine:",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 50.54,
      "end": 51.2,
      "text": "\"Yes,"
    },
    {
      "start": 51.24,
      "end": 51.6,
      "text": "sweetheart?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 53.0,
      "end": 55.86,
      "text": "She was a lanky sunburned girl whose tan dress of",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 55.96,
      "end": 59.24,
      "text": "thin woolen stuff clung to her with an effect of dampness."
    },
    {
      "start": 59.56,
      "end": 61.54,
      "text": "Her eyes were brown and playful"
    },
    {
      "start": 61.92,
      "end": 63.36,
      "text": "in a shiny boyish face."
    },
    {
      "start": 64.36,
      "end": 65.98,
      "text": "She finished shutting the door behind her,"
    },
    {
      "start": 66.04,
      "end": 66.92,
      "text": "leaned against it,"
    },
    {
      "start": 66.96,
      "end": 67.26,
      "text": "and said:"
    },
    {
      "start": 68.384,
      "end": 69.68,
      "text": "\"There's a girl wants to see you."
    },
    {
      "start": 69.78,
      "end": 71.02,
      "text": "Her name's Wonderly.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 72.22,
      "end": 72.7,
      "text": "\"A customer?\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 74.2,
      "end": 74.78,
      "text": "\"I guess so.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 75.0,
      "end": 75.58,
      "text": "You'll want"
    },
    {
      "start": 75.7,
      "end": 76.28,
      "text": "to see her anyway:"
    },
    {
      "start": 76.52,
      "end": 77.52,
      "text": "she's a knockout.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 78.688,
      "end": 79.12,
      "text": "\"Shoo her in,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 79.14,
      "end": 79.38,
      "text": "darling,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 79.62,
      "end": 80.3,
      "text": "said Spade."
    },
    {
      "start": 80.48,
      "end": 81.62,
      "text": "\"Shoo her in.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 83.168,
      "end": 84.64,
      "text": "Effie Perine opened the door again,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 84.96,
      "end": 87.16,
      "text": "following it back into the outer office,"
    },
    {
      "start": 87.5,
      "end": 89.56,
      "text": "standing with a hand on the knob while saying:"
    },
    {
      "start": 89.91,
      "end": 91.04,
      "text": "\"Will you come in,"
    },
    {
      "start": 91.1,
      "end": 91.64,
      "text": "Miss Wonderly?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 91.96,
      "end": 93.28,
      "text": "A voice said,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 93.76,
      "end": 94.36,
      "text": "\"Thank you,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 95.0,
      "end": 96.76,
      "text": "so softly that only the purest"
    },
    {
      "start": 96.76,
      "end": 98.9,
      "text": "articulation made the words intelligible,"
    },
    {
      "start": 99.62,
      "end": 101.24,
      "text": "and a young woman came through the doorway."
    },
    {
      "start": 102.02,
      "end": 102.86,
      "text": "She advanced slowly,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 103.04,
      "end": 103.96,
      "text": "with tentative steps,"
    },
    {
      "start": 104.88,
      "end": 106.34,
      "text": "looking at Spade with cobalt-blue"
    },
    {
      "start": 106.34,
      "end": 108.58,
      "text": "eyes that were both shy and probing."
    },
    {
      "start": 109.4,
      "end": 110.2,
      "text": "She was tall and"
    },
    {
      "start": 110.34,
      "end": 111.24,
      "text": "pliantly slender,"
    },
    {
      "start": 111.98,
      "end": 113.36,
      "text": "without angularity anywhere."
    },
    {
      "start": 113.93,
      "end": 115.94,
      "text": "Her body was erect and high-breasted,"
    },
    {
      "start": 116.14,
      "end": 117.08,
      "text": "her legs long,"
    },
    {
      "start": 117.22,
      "end": 118.46,
      "text": "her hands and feet narrow."
    },
    {
      "start": 119.4,
      "end": 120.84,
      "text": "She wore two shades of blue that had"
    },
    {
      "start": 120.84,
      "end": 122.46,
      "text": "been selected because of her eyes."
    },
    {
      "start": 123.34,
      "end": 126.54,
      "text": "The hair curling from under her blue hat was darkly red,"
    },
    {
      "start": 126.7,
      "end": 128.76,
      "text": "her full lips more brightly red."
    },
    {
      "start": 129.02,
      "end": 132.76,
      "text": "White teeth glistened in the crescent her timid smile made."
    },
    {
      "start": 133.856,
      "end": 134.44,
      "text": "Spade rose",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 134.56,
      "end": 136.94,
      "text": "bowing and indicating with a thick-fingered"
    },
    {
      "start": 136.94,
      "end": 139.42,
      "text": "hand the oaken armchair beside his desk."
    },
    {
      "start": 140.0,
      "end": 141.42,
      "text": "He was quite six feet tall."
    },
    {
      "start": 142.46,
      "end": 142.92,
      "text": "The steep"
    },
    {
      "start": 142.96,
      "end": 146.2,
      "text": "rounded slope of his shoulders made his body seem almost conical—"
    },
    {
      "start": 147.06,
      "end": 148.32,
      "text": "no broader than it was thick—"
    },
    {
      "start": 148.48,
      "end": 150.76,
      "text": "and kept his freshly pressed grey coat"
    },
    {
      "start": 151.28,
      "end": 152.22,
      "text": "from fitting very well."
    },
    {
      "start": 153.36,
      "end": 154.26,
      "text": "Miss Wonderly murmured,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 154.36,
      "end": 155.04,
      "text": "\"Thank you,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 155.51,
      "end": 159.32,
      "text": "softly as before and sat down on the edge of the chair's wooden seat."
    },
    {
      "start": 160.416,
      "end": 161.2,
      "text": "Spade sank into",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 161.2,
      "end": 161.98,
      "text": "his swivel-chair,"
    },
    {
      "start": 162.68,
      "end": 163.98,
      "text": "made a quarter-turn to face her,"
    },
    {
      "start": 164.08,
      "end": 165.16,
      "text": "smiled politely."
    },
    {
      "start": 165.48,
      "end": 167.46,
      "text": "He smiled without separating his"
    },
    {
      "start": 167.58,
      "end": 167.72,
      "text": "lips."
    },
    {
      "start": 168.48,
      "end": 170.18,
      "text": "All the v's in his face grew longer."
    },
    {
      "start": 170.98,
      "end": 173.88,
      "text": "The tappity-tap-tap and the thin bell and muffled",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 173.9,
      "end": 177.22,
      "text": "whir of Effie Perine's typewriting came through the closed door."
    },
    {
      "start": 178.336,
      "end": 179.6,
      "text": "Somewhere in a neighboring office,"
    },
    {
      "start": 179.76,
      "end": 181.74,
      "text": "a power-driven machine vibrated dully."
    },
    {
      "start": 182.78,
      "end": 183.66,
      "text": "On Spade's desk"
    },
    {
      "start": 183.76,
      "end": 185.74,
      "text": "a limp cigarette smoldered in a brass tray"
    },
    {
      "start": 185.94,
      "end": 187.46,
      "text": "filled with the remains of limp cigarettes."
    },
    {
      "start": 188.672,
      "end": 191.4,
      "text": "Ragged grey flakes of cigarette-ash dotted the yellow"
    },
    {
      "start": 191.48,
      "end": 195.1,
      "text": "top of the desk and the green blotter and the papers that were there."
    },
    {
      "start": 195.9,
      "end": 197.16,
      "text": "A buff-curtained window,"
    },
    {
      "start": 197.36,
      "end": 198.46,
      "text": "eight or ten inches open,"
    },
    {
      "start": 198.66,
      "end": 200.92,
      "text": "let in from the court a current of air"
    },
    {
      "start": 201.08,
      "end": 202.18,
      "text": "faintly scented with ammonia."
    },
    {
      "start": 203.04,
      "end": 205.94,
      "text": "The ashes on the desk twitched and crawled in the current."
    },
    {
      "start": 206.96,
      "end": 208.38,
      "text": "Miss Wonderly watched the grey flakes",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 208.56,
      "end": 209.16,
      "text": "twitch and crawl."
    },
    {
      "start": 209.5,
      "end": 210.84,
      "text": "Her eyes were uneasy."
    },
    {
      "start": 211.98,
      "end": 213.54,
      "text": "She sat on the very edge of the chair."
    },
    {
      "start": 213.76,
      "end": 214.8,
      "text": "Her feet were flat"
    },
    {
      "start": 214.8,
      "end": 215.32,
      "text": "on the floor,"
    },
    {
      "start": 215.48,
      "end": 216.86,
      "text": "as if she were about to rise."
    },
    {
      "start": 217.16,
      "end": 220.36,
      "text": "Her hands in dark gloves clasped a flat"
    },
    {
      "start": 220.44,
      "end": 221.08,
      "text": "dark handbag"
    },
    {
      "start": 221.08,
      "end": 221.62,
      "text": "in her lap."
    },
    {
      "start": 223.008,
      "end": 224.7,
      "text": "Spade rocked back in his chair and asked:",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 224.82,
      "end": 225.32,
      "text": "\"Now,"
    },
    {
      "start": 226.14,
      "end": 227.0,
      "text": "what can I do for you,"
    },
    {
      "start": 227.08,
      "end": 227.64,
      "text": "Miss Wonderly?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 228.88,
      "end": 230.24,
      "text": "She caught her breath and looked at him.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 231.06,
      "end": 232.37,
      "text": "She swallowed and said hurriedly:"
    },
    {
      "start": 232.83,
      "end": 234.64,
      "text": "\"Could you—? I"
    },
    {
      "start": 235.2,
      "end": 235.82,
      "text": "thought—I—"
    },
    {
      "start": 236.74,
      "end": 239.62,
      "text": "that is—\" Then she tortured her lower"
    },
    {
      "start": 239.62,
      "end": 241.16,
      "text": "lip with glistening teeth and said"
    },
    {
      "start": 241.28,
      "end": 241.58,
      "text": "nothing."
    },
    {
      "start": 242.74,
      "end": 245.41,
      "text": "Only her dark eyes spoke now, pleading."
    },
    {
      "start": 246.16,
      "end": 248.24,
      "text": "Spade smiled and nodded as if he understood her,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 248.38,
      "end": 251.1,
      "text": "but pleasantly, as if nothing serious were involved."
    },
    {
      "start": 251.74,
      "end": 254.84,
      "text": "He said: \"Suppose you tell me about it, from the"
    },
    {
      "start": 254.92,
      "end": 257.68,
      "text": "beginning, and then we'll know what needs doing."
    },
    {
      "start": 258.58,
      "end": 259.98,
      "text": "Better begin as far back as you can.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 261.44,
      "end": 261.82,
      "text": "\"That was in",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 261.96,
      "end": 262.3,
      "text": "New York.\""
    }
  ]
}